import React from 'react'
import {Container ,LeftContainer ,RightConatainer ,ImgBaner,Button ,Text,Desc,Input ,InputGroup} from './style'
import brands from '../../Rasim/brands.png'
const Show = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
               <LeftContainer>
                  <Text> Awesome tools for Designer & Developer.</Text>
                  <Desc>Antool is a web collection of information on paid or free Design and Development tools</Desc>
                  <InputGroup>
                   <Input placeholder="find more than 430+ tools..."/>
                   <Button> Search</Button>
                  </InputGroup>
               </LeftContainer>

               <RightConatainer>
                  <ImgBaner src={brands}/>
               </RightConatainer>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Show
